16:29.230 --> 16:30.436
[clears throat]

16:30.490 --> 16:31.980
Its true.

16:33.860 --> 16:36.021
I sold the mill for 1% equity
in Landry Enterprises.

16:36.070 --> 16:37.867
You sold the mill?

16:39.040 --> 16:40.940
Why would you sell--?

16:41.000 --> 16:42.786
Everything you went through
to get it off the ground.

16:42.830 --> 16:44.821
Everything those people
put you through.

16:44.870 --> 16:46.371
Put us through.

16:46.420 --> 16:47.956
Queen Sugar was about
to be ruined

16:48.000 --> 16:49.490
by that family
just on lies alone.

16:49.550 --> 16:51.916
