to taking back the power.

16:56.390 --> 16:58.130
[Nova]
So, you betray our family,

16:58.180 --> 17:00.808
get in bed with the enemy,
and all you got was 1%?

17:01.980 --> 17:03.436
Thats what were worth?

17:03.480 --> 17:04.845
[Charley]
I didnt betray anyone.

17:04.890 --> 17:06.141
And you aint try
and stop it?

17:06.190 --> 17:08.397
You knew about this?

17:08.440 --> 17:10.522
