-You sound crazy.

17:17.120 --> 17:18.906
[Charley] You dont think
Ive thought this through?

17:18.950 --> 17:21.327
1% gets me access.

17:21.370 --> 17:23.531
And every day, that access
gives me information

17:23.580 --> 17:25.787
