Sams hands was all in it.

18:40.030 --> 18:42.908
Now, look here,
I may not be a Bordelon,

18:42.950 --> 18:45.157
-but even I walked away.
-Right. Youre not a Bordelon.

18:45.200 --> 18:47.612
-You did not just--
-Now you hold on right there.

18:47.660 --> 18:50.993
Hollywood is as much family as
anybody sitting at this table,

18:51.040 --> 18:53.281
and you ought
to pay attention

18:53.340 --> 18:56.207
