to talk some sense into you.

19:01.890 --> 19:04.302
I am the only person
at this table doing something,

19:04.350 --> 19:05.886
doing anything...

19:06.980 --> 19:08.629
for Daddy.

19:12.770 --> 19:14.260
-Come on, Micah. Were leaving.
-No,no.

19:14.320 --> 19:17.141
