and finish explaining

19:17.190 --> 19:19.146
how you think
sitting at a table

19:19.200 --> 19:22.567
with folks that have preyed
on your family for generations

19:22.620 --> 19:23.985
makes good sense.

19:24.030 --> 19:25.327
Micah, come on.

19:30.000 --> 19:31.706
Micah.

19:31.750 --> 19:35.083
Hey, there
Little sister

19:35.130 --> 19:36.950
What you doing here?

19:38.880 --> 19:42.043
Cant you see theres trouble
In the air?

19:43.300 --> 19:45.211
[door opens]

19:45.260 --> 19:47.216
[door slams]

19:47.270 --> 19:49.226
