19:52.600 --> 19:54.682
You better run

19:54.730 --> 19:56.470
Yall have a good time.

19:56.520 --> 19:58.317
Hang on, little sister

19:58.360 --> 19:59.645
[door opens]

19:59.690 --> 20:01.601
