Johnny came through

20:54.290 --> 20:55.621
and messed it all up.

20:55.670 --> 20:57.456
No, Johnny won
fair and square.

20:57.500 --> 21:00.207
Youre just saying that
because he was your partner.

21:00.250 --> 21:02.218
I could beat you
with any partner.

21:02.260 --> 21:04.421
-[scoffs]
-Hi, Im Trinh.

21:04.470 --> 21:06.131
Ralph Angel.

21:06.180 --> 21:08.421
You the daughter
from up north, huh?

21:08.470 --> 21:10.131
I see Im famous.

21:10.180 --> 21:12.091
Yeah she went and got herself
a fancy degree

21:12.140 --> 21:14.552
so she dont have
to handle fish.

21:14.600 --> 21:16.807
Your mamas always talking
about you. Shes real proud.

21:16.850 --> 21:19.432
