last name?

21:33.330 --> 21:34.957
Bordelon.

21:35.000 --> 21:37.127
Bordelon...

21:37.170 --> 21:39.377
Hope Khanh hasnt been running
off his mouth too much.

21:39.420 --> 21:42.048
No, he good.

21:42.090 --> 21:44.331
