to his face?

21:54.430 --> 21:55.636
Touch.

21:55.690 --> 21:57.590
I got sisters.

21:57.650 --> 22:00.107
I know what its like
being the little bro.

22:00.150 --> 22:03.688
Big sisters just know how much
potential little brothers have.

22:06.530 --> 22:08.942
Ma said youve got a son.

22:09.910 --> 22:11.366
Yeah. Blue.

22:12.790 --> 22:13.905
Yeah, he in the car
right now,

22:13.950 --> 22:15.190
talking to his mama.

22:15.250 --> 22:16.706
Blue.

22:16.750 --> 22:18.286
I like that.

22:20.080 --> 22:22.492
-Good kid.
-Hey, Trinh,

22:22.550 --> 22:24.700
you going to keep passing out
those checks or what?

22:24.760 --> 22:27.331
Better get going
before they start a riot.

22:29.550 --> 22:31.381
Ill see you soon,
Miss Trinh.

22:31.430 --> 22:33.057
Ill be here.

22:34.390 --> 22:35.550
[Ralph Angel]
All right, now.

22:38.850 --> 22:41.182
-[indistinct chatter]
-[hip-hop music playing]

22:44.980 --> 22:47.278
Yeah, Wood was always cracking
jokes in the back of class.

22:47.320 --> 22:48.856
