22:48.910 --> 22:50.059
theyd kick him out
instead of me.

22:50.110 --> 22:51.361
[all laugh]

22:51.410 --> 22:52.980
Champagne?

22:54.120 --> 22:55.530
No, thank you.

22:55.580 --> 22:57.491
Oh, baby,
one wont hurt none.

22:57.540 --> 23:00.202
I dont need no liquor
to have fun with you, baby.

23:01.540 --> 23:03.371
[Gina]
Whens the big day?

23:03.420 --> 23:04.956
[Violet] Oh, well, were still
looking at venues.

23:05.000 --> 23:06.410
You going to have it
in St. Jo?

23:06.460 --> 23:08.121
St. Jo might be too small

23:08.170 --> 23:10.172
for what were
trying to do.

23:10.220 --> 23:13.542
Hell, we might go back to Italy,
make it a destination wedding.

23:13.600 --> 23:14.840
Fly the whole
family out.

23:14.890 --> 23:17.381
Youve done
struck gold.

23:17.430 --> 23:19.136
