23:19.190 --> 23:21.010
Ha! Now you the one
with the jokes.

23:21.060 --> 23:22.891
[all laugh]

23:22.940 --> 23:24.817
Wait a minute, is that
my high school sweetheart?

23:24.860 --> 23:26.566
Holleood!

23:26.610 --> 23:28.237
Come here.

23:28.280 --> 23:30.851
Oh, look at you.

23:30.910 --> 23:32.275
Ooh.

23:33.910 --> 23:35.446
Long time no see.

23:35.490 --> 23:37.492
Where you been keeping
your fine self?

23:37.540 --> 23:39.201
[Hollywood]
Good to see you too, Charmaine.

23:39.250 --> 23:41.411
Hey, girl. Hallelujah and amen
to this dress.

23:41.460 --> 23:44.088
Three months senior year.
Wasnt nothing.

23:50.680 --> 23:54.468
[door opens and closes]

23:56.350 --> 23:59.092
They on their high horses.

23:59.140 --> 24:00.846
Thats for sure.

24:04.770 --> 24:07.318
When it comes down to it,

24:07.360 --> 24:09.601
youre the only one
on the battle lines.

24:16.740 --> 24:18.947
Micah went off
with his friends.

24:21.500 --> 24:24.321
Wants to stay over
at Novas.

24:24.380 --> 24:26.496
He shouldnt
have heard all that.

24:26.540 --> 24:28.371
Hes almost 17.

24:30.260 --> 24:34.674
I cant protect him
from the world anymore.

24:36.180 --> 24:37.807
You know?

24:37.850 --> 24:39.169
Yeah.

24:42.100 --> 24:43.431
Ijust...

24:46.980 --> 24:49.892
I just dont want him
to hate me.

24:52.990 --> 24:56.027
Nah, he dont.

24:58.780 --> 25:00.782
Everything yall
been through...

25:02.330 --> 25:04.571
you aint nothing
but strength for that boy.

25:04.620 --> 25:06.326
He know it.

25:08.250 --> 25:09.547
And all this...

25:11.300 --> 25:13.586
all this,
youre doing this for him.

25:16.340 --> 25:20.344
Building a world
thats fair, just.

25:20.390 --> 25:22.130
Its for him.

25:22.180 --> 25:23.670
His legacy.

25:26.560 --> 25:27.936
No.

25:28.980 --> 25:30.470
You good.

25:32.030 --> 25:33.816
All right?

25:34.860 --> 25:36.270
Hey...

25:46.670 --> 25:47.989
