27:38.610 --> 27:43.274
But when I tried to tell you,
you were with some lady.

27:48.200 --> 27:49.656
[sighs]

27:51.250 --> 27:53.536
Everybody has accidents.

27:53.580 --> 27:56.208
There aint no shame about it.

27:56.250 --> 27:58.298
Just got to keep coming to me,
okay?

27:58.340 --> 28:01.832
Ill be there for you always,
you hear me?

28:03.470 --> 28:05.426
What if I have
another accident?

28:05.470 --> 28:07.210
Then well clean it up.

28:07.260 --> 28:08.670
Start fresh tomorrow.

28:10.180 --> 28:13.479
Come on, you can sleep
with me tonight.

28:17.730 --> 28:19.277
[grunts]

28:20.360 --> 28:21.770
[sighs]

28:21.820 --> 28:23.651
[hip-hop music playing]

28:23.700 --> 28:25.236
[Hollywood]
Coliseum.

28:27.200 --> 28:29.577
What you know about
the Leaning Tower of Pisa?

28:29.620 --> 28:31.110
-That its leaning.
-[laughs]

28:31.160 --> 28:32.570
