28:34.750 --> 28:37.799
Im sorry I didnt get a chance
to say hello to you back there.

28:37.840 --> 28:39.546
Its been so long,

28:39.590 --> 28:41.751
but I think we met
when I was in high school.

28:41.800 --> 28:43.677
