some water.

30:08.220 --> 30:10.097
Yall do your thing.

30:27.030 --> 30:29.407
Yo, Im telling yall,
she likes all my pics.

30:29.450 --> 30:30.940
Shes feeling me.
She likes my videos...

30:30.990 --> 30:33.402
[overlapped chatter]

30:33.450 --> 30:35.748
She be liking everybodys
photos. You are not special.

30:35.790 --> 30:37.576
[indistinct chatter]

30:41.250 --> 30:42.490
[camera shutters click]

30:42.550 --> 30:44.541
All right, who got next?

30:44.590 --> 30:46.080
-I|| go.
-Really?

30:46.130 --> 30:47.415
Yeah.

30:47.470 --> 30:49.210
You might want
to go slow.

30:49.260 --> 30:50.579
Girl, bye.

30:50.640 --> 30:52.039
Didnt I teach you?

30:52.100 --> 30:54.216
-Right?
-You right. You right.

30:54.270 --> 30:55.669
I know.

30:57.520 --> 30:58.885
All right, be careful.

30:58.940 --> 31:00.896
Lets see what you got.

31:07.110 --> 31:08.816
So, why are you here?

31:08.860 --> 31:10.521
Really?

31:10.570 --> 31:14.574
Like, who leaves
Gardini for St. Jo?

31:16.080 --> 31:17.741
You miss being around
your people that much?

31:17.790 --> 31:20.247
No, Ive never really
been around my people.

31:21.580 --> 31:22.990
You know what I mean?

31:23.040 --> 31:24.120
I never couldve
rallied a group

31:24.170 --> 31:25.910
to kneel at a game,

31:25.960 --> 31:28.542
or protest police brutality
at my old school.

31:28.590 --> 31:30.080
-So...
-Hey, man,

31:30.130 --> 31:31.210
everybody was talking
about that.

31:31.260 --> 31:32.716
Yeah, exactly, man.

31:32.760 --> 31:34.045
You know?

31:34.100 --> 31:35.886
Fight for what
you believe in,

31:35.930 --> 31:39.684
and dont care who it scares
or makes uncomfortable.

31:39.730 --> 31:41.766
Right. Thats whats up, man.

31:41.810 --> 31:43.550
We got to figure out
what we doing next.

31:43.610 --> 31:45.316
Yeah, but we got to level up
next time.

31:45.360 --> 31:48.022
Didnt yall just get suspended?

31:48.070 --> 31:50.607
Man, I dont care
about getting suspended.

31:50.650 --> 31:52.447
Yeah, facts.
Look, we aint no bitches.

31:52.490 --> 31:54.321
All right? But look,
we cant be doing nothing

31:54.370 --> 31:56.440
to get my ass picked up
by Truancy again.

31:56.490 --> 31:58.287
-My mom aint with that.
-No, no, no.

31:58.330 --> 32:00.787
But we still going to take it
to the rest of St. Jo.

32:00.830 --> 32:02.741
-Right.
-Yeah, for real.

32:02.790 --> 32:04.781
Dont sleep on the resistance,
you know what Im saying?

32:04.840 --> 32:06.660
I got to put this on Snap,
know what Im saying?

32:06.710 --> 32:09.668
Dont sleep on the resistance...

32:09.720 --> 32:11.210
[overlapped chatter]

32:11.260 --> 32:12.500
-Coming at you.
-Resistance.

32:12.550 --> 32:14.290
