Hes a talker.
[laughs]

33:06.190 --> 33:08.818
I done told every joke, story,
anecdote that I know.

33:08.860 --> 33:10.396
Hmm.

33:13.820 --> 33:17.563
So, maybe,
if its all right with you...

33:20.120 --> 33:22.782
we could call it a night.

33:24.420 --> 33:28.493
And I can take my beautiful,
sew fiance home.

33:36.260 --> 33:37.750
Hmm.

33:37.800 --> 33:39.802
Im _fine with that
If you are.

33:39.850 --> 33:41.169
Yeah.

33:42.350 --> 33:43.726
Lets get out of here.

33:43.770 --> 33:45.931
[grunts]

33:59.700 --> 34:01.577
Ginger tea.

34:03.370 --> 34:04.906
I can put those four-wheeling
clothes in the wash.

34:04.960 --> 34:06.666
No, Im good.

34:10.210 --> 34:12.622
We may not always agree
with what she does,

34:12.670 --> 34:17.209
but we can agree it comes from
a place of love.

34:17.260 --> 34:19.046
A love of herself?

34:19.970 --> 34:21.380
Power?

34:21.430 --> 34:23.386
-Micah...
-Nobody asked her

34:23.430 --> 34:26.433
to sell out her own
so she can beg for, what, 1%?

34:27.850 --> 34:29.511
I mean, you said it
yourself.

34:30.980 --> 34:32.811
Maybe I shouldnt
have said it.

34:32.860 --> 34:36.773
Look, I dont agree
with your moms methods,

34:36.820 --> 34:40.062
but this...
this aint new.

34:40.120 --> 34:42.486
King. Malcolm.

34:42.530 --> 34:44.532
Medgar Evers.
Whitney Young.

34:44.580 --> 34:46.457
Some wanted
to storm the gates.

34:46.500 --> 34:50.038
Others wanted a seat
at the table.

34:50.080 --> 34:52.287
But they all wanted
the same thing:

34:52.340 --> 34:55.127
dignity and freedom.

34:57.510 --> 35:00.297
See, thats-- why couldnt
she be more like you?

35:00.340 --> 35:02.843
Hey, dont do that.

35:02.890 --> 35:04.551
Im serious.

35:04.600 --> 35:07.763
You have an incredible
platform, you know?

35:07.810 --> 35:09.937
And you make change
with words and actions,

35:09.980 --> 35:12.517
not secrets and lies,
and...

35:12.560 --> 35:15.222
You be proud of your mama.

35:15.280 --> 35:17.066
Shes achieved more
in her lifetime

35:17.110 --> 35:19.943
than most people dream of.

35:19.990 --> 35:21.981
I am proud. Its just...

35:25.290 --> 35:27.246
I am proud.

35:27.290 --> 35:30.248
And you do know
I quit my job.

35:30.290 --> 35:32.030
Yeah, but you got
that book deal.

35:34.000 --> 35:37.379
You can write about the black
farmers and their struggles.

35:39.130 --> 35:40.791
You could write
about anything you want.

35:51.520 --> 35:55.513
It seems impossible
Until its done

35:57.900 --> 36:01.313
Mandela said it well

36:01.360 --> 36:03.362
And its begun

36:05.330 --> 36:08.618
The fights unbeatable
Until youve won

36:09.830 --> 36:11.866
So keep on fighting

36:13.920 --> 36:15.740
Keep on fighting

36:18.340 --> 36:23.334
Keep your sunshine
Right inside your smile

36:23.390 --> 36:26.462
Open wide, seek a life

36:26.510 --> 36:30.594
Through your eyes
In the night

36:30.640 --> 36:33.097
As you shine

36:34.610 --> 36:37.647
Make it all
What you are

36:47.030 --> 36:48.736
[chimes and vibrates]

37:10.470 --> 37:12.472
What up?

37:12.520 --> 37:15.057
I hope you aint
wore out already.

37:15.100 --> 37:16.431
[laughs]

37:17.900 --> 37:19.970
I meant to text you,
but...

37:21.280 --> 37:23.145
tonight aint no good.

37:24.450 --> 37:25.940
My bad.

37:33.080 --> 37:34.786
I appreciate it.

37:36.040 --> 37:37.996
I do.

37:40.300 --> 37:42.291
But Blue aint sleep yet.

37:42.340 --> 37:43.659
You know how it is.

37:45.300 --> 37:48.463
I do.
Simones over at her dads.

37:49.970 --> 37:51.460
Yeah.

37:53.140 --> 37:55.131
Im going to be taking it
easy for a while,

37:55.190 --> 37:56.805
SO...

37:56.850 --> 37:58.647
Okay.

37:58.690 --> 38:00.976
Well, you know what
youre missing out on, so...

38:01.020 --> 38:02.180
[laughs]

38:02.230 --> 38:03.686
Come on, now.

38:03.740 --> 38:05.310
Its all right.

38:05.360 --> 38:07.351
You go on and be a good dad.

38:08.820 --> 38:10.572
Ill see you.

38:43.030 --> 38:44.395
Im sorry.

38:45.740 --> 38:47.640
Its cool.

38:53.660 --> 38:55.696
You werent supposed
to find out.

38:57.290 --> 38:59.030
At least not now.

39:02.130 --> 39:03.586
But Im glad you did.

39:03.630 --> 39:05.291
Why?

39:05.340 --> 39:07.331
The worlds not perfect.

39:07.380 --> 39:09.257
You know that.

39:09.300 --> 39:14.499
So I dont know why we expect
our solutions to be.

39:19.140 --> 39:20.687
If youre going to keep
doing this,

39:20.730 --> 39:22.800
can you at least
promise to win?

39:22.860 --> 39:26.352
I promise that it will all
have been worth it.

39:30.070 --> 39:31.947
I trust you.

39:42.500 --> 39:44.741
[Ralph Angel]
I need to know you going
to take this serious.

39:44.800 --> 39:46.700
Look, man, I been going
through it since I got out.

39:46.760 --> 39:49.126
But I keep
my nose clean.

39:51.510 --> 39:52.829
What you was in for?

39:54.470 --> 39:55.676
[sighs]

39:55.720 --> 39:57.347
Stealing cars.

39:57.390 --> 39:59.381
Selling parts.

40:07.070 --> 40:08.890
Well, its slow work
around here.

40:10.030 --> 40:11.349
Aint no quick cash.

40:12.780 --> 40:14.987
I aint looking
for no short cuts.

40:16.370 --> 40:18.190
I aint going back.

40:25.040 --> 40:26.496
[clears throat]

40:32.380 --> 40:34.462
Fill this out.

40:34.510 --> 40:36.592
Get it back to me
soon as you can.

40:39.220 --> 40:40.881
[clears throat]

40:42.140 --> 40:43.801
[sighs]

40:45.690 --> 40:47.100
See you tomorrow.

40:47.150 --> 40:49.357
Bright and early.

40:51.400 --> 40:53.197
On time.

40:53.240 --> 40:56.232
Yes, sir. On time.

40:57.870 --> 40:59.531
All right, now.

41:00.750 --> 41:02.365
[sighs]

41:03.750 --> 41:05.786
Take me down in flames

41:05.830 --> 41:07.286
[car door closes]

41:07.340 --> 41:08.989
[Dana]

41:13.050 --> 41:15.041
-[B|ue] Mommy!
-[Darla] Aww!

41:15.090 --> 41:17.046
I missed you a lot.

41:17.100 --> 41:19.921
Hey, let me take
a look at you.

41:19.970 --> 41:22.552
Oh, my goodness.
Youve gotten so big.

41:23.850 --> 41:25.260
I missed you so much.

41:25.310 --> 41:26.937
I missed you too.

41:28.520 --> 41:32.024
Take away the pain

41:32.070 --> 41:35.233
Pull it from my vein

41:35.280 --> 41:38.067
Touch me like you do

41:39.620 --> 41:41.440
Fall right back to you

41:44.750 --> 41:48.959
Well, dont tell me
This doesnt feel right

41:51.880 --> 41:56.465
Because Im thinking
About it every night

42:09.900 --> 42:12.642
Yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah

42:15.360 --> 42:17.316
Mmm
